#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"In this guide, you'll create a REST endpoint, see live coding in action, add a service with dependency injection, and write tests.\n"
"You won't write any boilerplate, and you won't have to restart the app, not even once."
msgstr "在本指南中，您将创建一个 REST 端点，观看实时编码演示，添加一个采用依赖注入的服务，并编写测试用例。您无需编写任何冗余代码，也无需重启应用程序——甚至一次都不用。"

