#: _versions/main/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`quarkus:dev` runs Quarkus in development mode.\n"
"Edit your Java files or resource files, save, and refresh your browser, changes take effect immediately, no restart needed.\n"
"If there are any issues with compilation or deployment an error page will let you know."
msgstr "`quarkus:dev` 会在开发模式下运行 Quarkus。编辑 Java 文件或资源文件，保存后刷新浏览器，更改会立即生效，无需重启。如果编译或部署过程中出现任何问题，系统会通过错误页面通知您。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Try it: open `src/main/java/org/acme/GreetingResource.java`, change `\"Hello from Quarkus REST\"` to `\"Hola from Quarkus\"`, save, and refresh http://localhost:8080/hello.\n"
"Then, switch back to `\"Hello from Quarkus REST\"`, refresh again... changed again!"
msgstr "试一试：打开 `src/main/java/org/acme/GreetingResource.java` ，将 `“Hello from Quarkus REST”` 改为 `“Hola from Quarkus”，` 保存后刷新 http://localhost:8080/hello 。 然后，将内容切换回 `“Hello from Quarkus REST”，` 再次刷新……​又变回来了！"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/getting-started.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "While dev mode is running, open http://localhost:8080/q/dev-ui/[the Dev UI], a dashboard where you can browse installed extensions, configuration, endpoints, and more, all live-updated as you code."
msgstr "在开发者模式运行期间，打开 link:http://localhost:8080/q/dev-ui/[开发者界面] （ link:http://localhost:8080/q/dev-ui/[Dev UI] ）——这是一个仪表盘，您可以在其中浏览已安装的扩展程序、配置、端点等内容，所有内容都会随着您的编码实时更新。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/getting-started.adoc
msgid ""
"This will also listen for a debugger on port `5005`. If you want to wait for the debugger to attach before running you\n"
"can pass `-Dsuspend` on the command line. If you don't want the debugger at all you can use `-Ddebug=false`."
msgstr "这也将在端口 `5005` 上监听调试器。如果你想在运行前等待调试器的连接，你可以在命令行中传递 `-Dsuspend` 。如果你根本不想要调试器，你可以使用 `-Ddebug=false` 。"

